:INFO
Client Management Templates and Frameworks
Communication templates and management frameworks for keeping client relationships healthy and professional throughout an engagement.

:TASK
[ ] Send project kickoff email within 24 hours of signing
[ ] Share onboarding questionnaire in week one
[ ] Set up shared project folder with client
[ ] Send weekly status update every Friday
[ ] Schedule mid-project check-in call at 50% milestone
[ ] Deliver retrospective document at project close
[ ] Request testimonial within one week of delivery
[ ] Propose next engagement within two weeks of close

:NOTE
The weekly status update is the most important communication habit. Even when nothing is blocked, a short update builds trust and prevents the anxiety that leads to micromanagement from the client side.

